den-president\/","shortlink":"http:\/\/ti.me\/1IfTlFz","title":"Beau Biden&#8217;s Dying Wish Was for His Dad to Run for President, Report Says","friendly_title":"Beau Biden\u2019s Dying Wish Was for His Dad to Run for President, Report Says","post_type":"post","available":true,"time_article":true,"comments_allowed":true,"show_comments":true,"short_title":"Beau Biden&#8217;s Dying Wish Was for His Dad to Run for President, Report Says","excerpt":"Joe Biden is reportedly considering running in 2016","format":"brief","time":{"pretty":"3:08 PM ET","published":"2015-08-01 15:08:03","updated":"2015-08-01 19:08:03","minute":"3:08 pm","short":"3:08 PM ET"},"authors":[{"id":208186494,"url":"http:\/\/time.com\/author\/eliza-gray\/","name":"Eliza Gray","bio":"","short_bio":"","types":["time staff"],"twitter":"elizalgray","twitter_url":"https:\/\/twitter.com\/elizalgray","gplus":"","fb":"","email":"","thumbnail":"http:\/\/i0.wp.com\/timedotcom.files.wordpress.com\/2014\/03\/mg_1432_new.jpg?crop=347px%2C318px%2C2874px%2C2874px&resize=100%2C100&quality=65&strip=color","contributor":true,"search_link":"http:\/\/search.time.com\/results.html?Ntt=Eliza+Gray"}],"content":"<aside class=\"right-rail__container right-rail__container--ad\"><div class=\"right-rail__ad__wrapper right-rail__module\"><div class=\"right-rail__ad\" id=\"right-rail__ad-3981228\"><\/div><\/div><\/aside>\n<p>Vice President Joe Biden&#8217;s late son Beau told his father to run for president before he died, according to a report.<\/p>\n<p>New York<em> Times<\/em> columnist Maureen Dowd, in her <a href=\"http:\/\/www.nytimes.com\/2015\/08\/02\/opinion\/sunday\/maureen-dowd-joe-biden-in-2016-what-would-beau-do.html?_r=0\">weekend column<\/a> entitled &#8220;Joe Biden in 2016: What Would Beau Do?,&#8221; describes, in great detail, a conversation that Beau had with his father before dying, urging his father to run for president rather than letting the office fall to former Secretary of State Hillary Clinton. Joseph &#8220;Beau&#8221; Biden III died of brain cancer at the end of May. Dowd&#8217;s source for the anecdote is not clear from the column.<\/p>\n<p>Vice President Biden has been holding meetings at his Washington home to discuss the possibility of a run, according to Dowd.<\/p>\n","read_more":true,"section":{"name":"Politics","slug":"politics","url":"http:\/\/time.com\/politics\/","description":"Political insight from the Beltway and beyond. Covering the White House, elections, primaries, Congress, domestic policy, foreign policy, the military and more","politics":true},"tag":{"name":"2016 Election","slug":"2016-election","url":"http:\/\/time.com\/tag\/2016-election\/"},"tags":"2016 Campaign|2016 Election|Hillary Clinton|Joe Biden","hero":{"class":"portrait","thumbnail":"http:\/\/i1.wp.com\/timedotcom.files.wordpress.com\/2015\/08\/beau-biden.jpg?crop=276px%2C0px%2C1627px%2C1628px&resize=100%2C100&quality=65&strip=color","src":{"small":"https:\/\/timedotcom.files.wordpress.com\/2015\/08\/beau-biden.jpg?quality=65&strip=color&w=280","small_2x":"https:\/\/timedotcom.files.wordpress.com\/2015\/08\/beau-biden.jpg?quality=65&strip=color&w=560","large":"https:\/\/timedotcom.files.wordpress.com\/2015\/08\/beau-biden.jpg?quality=65&strip=color&w=407","large_2x":"https:\/\/timedotcom.files.wordpress.com\/2015\/08\/beau-biden.jpg?quality=65&strip=color&w=814"},"credit":"Charles Dharapak\u2014AP","caption":"At the time of the photo, Democratic vice presidential candidate Sen. Joe Biden, embraces his son Beau on stage at the Democratic National Convention in Denver on Aug. 27, 2008. ","alt":"Beau Biden, Joe Biden","providers":[],"masonry":{"small_width":300,"small_height":342,"large_width":625,"large_height":713}},"id":3981228,"encoded_url":"http%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3981228%2Fbeau-biden-joe-biden-president%2F","encoded_shortlink":"http%3A%2F%2Fti.me%2F1IfTlFz","encoded_title":"Beau+Biden%E2%80%99s+Dying+Wish+Was+for+His+Dad+to+Run+for+President%2C+Report+Says","twitter_text":"Beau%